columns.name: UNIQUE ID
columns.description: Unique ID

columns.name: GENERATED ON
columns.description: Indicates the date and hour the entry was generated on.  All entries in a batch will contain the same generated_on stamp.

columns.name: SITE ID
columns.description: The LinkNYC Kiosk's unique identification number.  The Site ID includes the borough, community district, and PPT ID.

columns.name: STATUS
columns.description: Status of LinkNYC Kiosk location.

columns.name: PPT ID
columns.description: The ID number associated with the permit to operate public pay telephone service.  The PPT ID is the same as the ID for the public pay telephone the Link kiosk replaced.  New sites that don’t replace pay telephones receive new PPT IDs.

columns.name: Address
columns.description: The street associated with a building's street address and the name of the street that a site is located on.

columns.name: CITY
columns.description: Location in New York City

columns.name: STATE
columns.description: New York State

columns.name: POSTCODE
columns.description: Five (5) digit postal code assigned by the United States Postal Service.

columns.name: BOROUGH
columns.description: The New York City borough where the LinkNYC kiosks are located.

columns.name: LATITUDE
columns.description: Points that fall North or South of the Equator, expressed in degrees.

columns.name: LONGITUDE
columns.description: Points that fall East or West of the Prime Meridian, expressed in degrees.

columns.name: CROSS STREET 1
columns.description: One of the closest streets to a potential LinkNYC site.

columns.name: CROSS STREET 2
columns.description: One of the closest streets to a potential LinkNYC site.

columns.name: CORNER lOCATION
columns.description: The direction the LinkNYC Kiosk is facing.

columns.name: COMMUNITY BOARD
columns.description: Community Board: An appointed advisory group from a variety of districts throughout NYC's five boroughs.  They deal with issues such as zoning, land usage, and any other matter related to the quality of life of their residents.

columns.name: COUNCIL DISTRICT
columns.description: Council District is the lawmaking body of the City of New York.  There are 51 districts throughout NYC's five boroughs.

columns.name: CENSUS TRACT
columns.description: Permanent statistical subdivisions to provide a stable set of geographic units for the presentation of statistical data.

columns.name: NTA
columns.description: Neighborhood identifiers to differentiate NYC's five boroughs

columns.name: BBL
columns.description: Every real estate property is identified by a set of 3 numbers for taxes, zoning, construction, and other purposes.

columns.name: BIN
columns.description: Every real estate property has an assigned 7-digit number issued by the Department of City Planning.

columns.name: INSTALLATION DATE
columns.description: Date of LinkNYC was physically installed.

columns.name: ACTIVATION DATE
columns.description: Date of LinkNYC was physically activated.

columns.name: WIFI STATUS
columns.description: Enumerated value of ‘up’ or ‘down’ indicating last status of link’s Wi-Fi connection. The value 'null' will be assigned if link is not activated.

columns.name: WIFI LAST TS
columns.description: Indicates date and time for last WIFI status metric.  The value 'no poll' will be assigned if link is not activated or no status has been retrieved within last hour.

columns.name: TABLET STATUS
columns.description: Enumerated value of ‘up’ or ‘down’ indicating last status of link’s tablet. The value 'null' will be assigned if link is not activated.

columns.name: TABLET LAST TS
columns.description: Indicates date and time for last tablet status metric. The value 'no poll' will be assigned if link is not activated or no status has been retrieved within last hour.

columns.name: PHONE STATUS
columns.description: Enumerated value of ‘up’ or ‘down’ indicating last status of link’s dialer. The value 'null' will be assigned if link is not activated.

columns.name: DIALER LAST TS
columns.description: Indicates date and time for last dialer status metric. The value 'no poll' will be assigned if link is not activated or no status has been retrieved within last hour.
